data.description: Located in the heart of Avondale, this remarkable like new property offers a perfect balance of nature's charm and meticulous indoor maintenance! Inside you'll find a spacious great room, a chef's dream kitchen with a long island that adds a touch of luxury, and three bedrooms with two baths--It's a perfect family haven. As you step into the tranquil backyard, you'll find a peaceful oasis of greenery and serenity. This home is a true testament to pride of ownership in prime Avondale. Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own! ***Security system, Fridge, washer/dryer, water softener & RO system included***
